# food-contamination-line
- I saw @food-worker @food-contamination-action @prepared-food. @food-avoidance-reaction
- Apparently, @food-worker has been adding @contamination-material to @prepared-food. @food-avoidance-reaction
- The @prepared-food has @contamination-object in it today. @food-avoidance-reaction
- You didn't hear it from me, but @food-worker was carrying @contamination-container into @canteen-place. @rumour-ending
- Did you see what they put in @prepared-food? It looked like @contamination-material. @food-avoidance-reaction
- @uncertain-source that @prepared-food was exposed to @contamination-source. @rumour-ending

# food-contamination-action
- pour @contamination-liquid into
- stir @contamination-powder through
- press @contamination-paste beneath
- sprinkle @contamination-granules over
- inject @contamination-liquid into
- scrape @contamination-residue across
- empty @contamination-container-content into
- hide @contamination-solid inside
- drizzle @contamination-gel over
- mix @contamination-fibres through

