# food-avoidance-reaction
- I think I'll stick to @safe-food.
- Suddenly, @safe-food sounds pretty good.
- Maybe I will skip @meal-name.
- You can try it first.
- I am not touching that without gloves.
- That explains the smell, at least.
- I have completely lost my appetite.
- I knew the colour was suspicious.
- Remind me never to order it again.
- I may eat after my shift instead.
- The vending wall has never looked so inviting.
- I am beginning to miss military rations.

