# food-quality-line
- The @prepared-food tastes @taste-quality today. @food-quality-reaction
- I don't know how they made @prepared-food both @texture-quality and @taste-quality. @food-quality-reaction
- The portion looked @appearance-quality, but it tasted @taste-quality. @food-quality-reaction
- @uncertain-source that the recipe for @prepared-food came from @recipe-origin. That would explain a lot.
- I have eaten @prepared-food on three stations, and this is somehow the @quality-extreme version.

