- metallic
- aggressively sweet
- like warm plastic
- mostly of salt
- faintly medicinal
- better than it smells
- worse than it looks
- like somebody described garlic to a machine
- strangely nostalgic
- completely flavourless
- smoky for no clear reason
- like recycled air

