- faintly luminous
- much too colourful
- grey enough to be worrying
- professionally arranged
- as if it had moved recently
- surprisingly fresh
- exactly like insulation foam
- better than anything here usually looks
- old before it reached the table

# food-quality-reaction
- I finished it anyway.
- At least the portion was generous.
- I may need a stronger drink.
- Nobody else seemed bothered.
- The cook looked proud of it.
- It cost too much to leave unfinished.
- I have had worse, but not recently.
- My stomach is still deciding what it thinks.
- Next time I am ordering the simplest thing available.
- Somehow there was still a queue for seconds.

