- The ticket made it sound simple.
- At least I saw plenty of corridors.
- I am never complaining about planetary trains again.
- Nobody designs routes for people carrying luggage.
- The last connection was standing room only.
- It took longer than crossing the system.
- I met the same customs officer twice.

