- directly beside a lift motor
- surprisingly comfortable
- shaped like a storage locker
- missing half its furniture
- warm enough to grow vegetables
- colder than the cargo deck
- technically intended for two people
- at the end of six identical corridors
- slowly developing a smell

# cabin-consolation
- the door locks
- the lights mostly work
- the ventilation is quiet
- the previous tenant left a kettle
- the view screen shows the right planet
- nobody can find it without directions
- the bed is level
- the rent includes water

# cabin-problem
- vibrating
- leaking condensation
- displaying an old warning
- making @maintenance-sound
- losing power every night
- smelling like hot metal
- refusing to dim the lights
- reporting the wrong temperature
- locking the storage cupboard
- attracting cleaning drones

