# home-difference
- nights are actually dark
- rain makes the air smell clean
- you can walk without turning a corner
- food grows outdoors
- gravity never needs maintenance
- windows show the real sky
- nobody announces the weather
- directions include landmarks

# station-difference
- every hour has an announcement
- the weather comes from ventilation
- walking anywhere becomes a journey
- vegetables require security clearance
- gravity has office hours
- windows require a camera
- the sky is always on schedule
- landmarks move between shifts

